{"tid":877751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"央視記者在英毆香港籍學生 中方：香港事是中國內政","createTime":"2018-10-26T14:53:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T21:57:24.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ecacdb22c4271209d1e702c57f272d8747978f4f","tid":877751,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T14:53:31.000Z","msg":"央視記者在英毆香港籍學生 中方：香港事是中國內政<br />\n<br />\n2018-10-26 22:10<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國央視記者孔琳琳（Kong Linlin）先前出席英國伯明罕「香港自由、法治、自治受損」座談會，離場時還2度掌摑1名香港籍學生，被警方逮捕並吃上襲擊官司；中國外交部對此竟稱「香港事務是中國內政」。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人華春瑩指出，央視記者當時是「正當行使權利表達觀點卻遭百般阻撓」，且在現場經歷「粗暴對待」，不料現在卻被「顛倒黑白」，中方政府認為英國警察部門對此事件態度有所轉變，「原因令人置（質）疑」，因此希望該名央視記者能夠打贏官司。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩提到，英國當地的民間團體明目張膽地「鼓吹分裂中國」，中方對此「強烈譴責和堅決反對」，香港自1997年7月1日回歸中國已逾21年，當局認為歷史無法倒流，因此希望英國政府能夠身體力行與中國保持良好態度，「香港事務是中國內政」。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;"},{"pid":"1ba3ef1d63f8f716f262a40e524ce5c8a7a4d223","tid":877751,"uid":188396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T14:57:13.000Z","msg":"基本法？一國兩制？真係笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過口交部咁講係咪違反中英聯合聲明（不過算啦英國唔會真係理+歷史文件）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b512aff73a69ffb7826c6111b445ce080262c5","tid":877751,"uid":216538,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T14:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/26/225747_8240e01951ecbcb0e5e9bf949cafce6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F26%2F225747_8240e01951ecbcb0e5e9bf949cafce6d.jpg&h=68cd90a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cce4b981b764eedb65dafd9787d38645026eb5ed","tid":877751,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T15:02:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.sinovision.net/attachments/2011/03/06/3113498384d73a7bf6ddd1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sinovision.net%2Fattachments%2F2011%2F03%2F06%2F3113498384d73a7bf6ddd1.jpg&h=9b97897a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"888f1bdf5b14bd0ef5fa6cdca7373c57aa2057e2","tid":877751,"uid":98386,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T15:05:18.000Z","msg":"有隻支那臭雞喺人地座談會上叫春係「正當行使權利表達觀點卻遭百般阻撓」，之後摑某人兩巴叫遭到「粗暴對待」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da420923b4e02d35bdb5b04cf56a81c3641c9b0d","tid":877751,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T15:30:50.000Z","msg":"咁全世界都係中國既領土黎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n英國係中國既領土，當然係中國內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6311f6772745c4d3f2c4048f05734a87f8af8076","tid":877751,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T18:41:18.000Z","msg":"係人地盤搞事仲咁囂張, 等陣英國制裁埋你我又有得笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe1ef1f081181ba88770124cf5c9fde65fae5e9f","tid":877751,"uid":8187,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T19:48:11.000Z","msg":"係英國犯法<br />\n竟然係中國內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個國家講句野出黎<br />\n同啲冇讀過書既人一樣<br />\n你中國冇法律姐<br />\n人地有架傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815a607ee411a1e3d588ba69089c7ffdd4dcb25d","tid":877751,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da420923b4e02d35bdb5b04cf56a81c3641c9b0d","tid":877751,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T15:30:50.000Z","msg":"咁全世界都係中國既領土黎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n英國係中國既領土，當然係中國內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T20:19:33.000Z","msg":"所以咪咁多洗頭艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img sr